fields.description:
Get a campaign and associated offers by a promo code

If campaign not found then you get

{
  "errors" : [
    {
      "message" : "Not found",
      "extensions" : {
        "code" : "NOT_FOUND"
      }
    }
  ]
}

Find a campaign by promo code if the code is applicable for existing user subscription

If passed promo code is invalid, you will get:
```
{
  "errors" : [
    {
      "message" : "Invalid promo code",
      "extensions" : {
        "code" : "INVALID_PROMO_CODE"
      }
    }
  ]
}
```

If there is no related Campaign found by promo code, you will get:
```
{
  "errors" : [
    {
      "message" : "Not found",
      "extensions" : {
        "code" : "NOT_FOUND"
      }
    }
  ]
}
```

If there is no applicable subscription found or applying promo code is impossible:
```
{
  "errors" : [
    {
      "message" : "Promo code cannot be consumed",
      "extensions" : {
        "code" : "PROMO_CODE_NOT_CONSUMABLE"
      }
    }
  ]
}
```

Unexpected errors look like this:
```
{
  "errors" : [
    {
      "message" : "Internal server error",
      "extensions" : {
        "code" : "INTERNAL_SERVER_ERROR"
      }
    }
  ]
}
```

If the passed promo code is invalid, you will get:
```
{
  "errors" : [
    {
      "message" : "Invalid promo code",
      "extensions" : {
        "code" : "INVALID_PROMO_CODE",
        "clientMutationId" : "client-mutation-id"
      }
    }
  ]
}
```

Failure to get promo code related Campaign, you will get:
```
