```
{
  "errors" : [
    {
      "message" : "Promo code cannot be consumed",
      "extensions" : {
        "code" : "PROMO_CODE_NOT_CONSUMABLE",
        "clientMutationId" : "client-mutation-id"
      }
    }
  ]
}
```

Unexpected errors look like this:
```
{
